OL,3,CThe tidal wave of desperation I've
OL,4,Cwitnessed reporting on SEND crisis
OL,6,FWhile many people live hugely
OL,7,Findependent and successful lives while
OL,8,Fhaving special educational needs -
OL,9,Fotherwise known as SEN or SEND - the
OL,10,Ffact is that others need considerable
OL,11,Fsupport.
OL,13,FFor children, they need an education
OL,14,Ftailored to them. The snag? At the
OL,15,Fmoment in Britain, it is often a huge
OL,16,Fbattle for parents to achieve that.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
