OL,3,CThe tidal wave of desperation I've
OL,4,Cwitnessed reporting on SEND crisis
OL,6,FWhen I first started meeting families
OL,7,Fwhose children were not in education
OL,8,Fit hit a nerve. These were children
OL,9,Fwith their whole lives ahead of them,
OL,10,Fbut those lives were essentially on
OL,11,Fpause.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
