OL,3,CThe tidal wave of desperation I've
OL,4,Cwitnessed reporting on SEND crisis
OL,6,FChildren with SEND will often struggle
OL,7,Fwith speech and language, their
OL,8,Fbehaviour, emotions and concentration.
OL,9,FThere are, of course, specialist
OL,10,Fschools that are designed to support
OL,11,Fchildren who are autistic, for
OL,12,Fexample, but the number of places are
OL,13,Flimited.
OL,15,FParents, therefore, have to fight the
OL,16,Fsystem. However, the system is
OL,17,Fcomplicated, full of jargon and legal
OL,18,Fcomplications and they find themselves
OL,19,Fup against local authorities who will
OL,20,Ffight them back.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
