OL,3,CThe tidal wave of desperation I've
OL,4,Cwitnessed reporting on SEND crisis
OL,6,FFor many the process often ends in
OL,7,Fcourt, with a tribunal deciding in
OL,8,Ffavour of one of the parties. Families
OL,9,Foften win at this stage, but by then
OL,10,Fso much time has passed with the child
OL,11,Fhaving had a broken or very limited
OL,12,Feducation to that point.
OL,14,FI have found the process of reporting
OL,15,Fon this issue both heartbreaking and
OL,16,Fincredibly important. It is
OL,17,Fheartbreaking when a mum tells you her
OL,18,Fdaughter simply is not happy, as Ellie
OL,19,FElliott from Somerton did.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
