OL,3,CThe tidal wave of desperation I've
OL,4,Cwitnessed reporting on SEND crisis
OL,6,FI met with Ellie in August 2023 as her
OL,7,Fdaughter faced the upcoming academic
OL,8,Fyear without a school place. She told
OL,9,Fme: "She's so, so far behind where you
OL,10,Fwould hope for a child her age to be
OL,11,Fand it just affects everything in her
OL,12,Flife. And she's not happy."
OL,14,FIn 2022, I met the Barnes family from
OL,15,FHighbridge who told me about the
OL,16,Fimpact of large class sizes and how
OL,17,Fthe setup of mainstream schools makes
OL,18,Fit very hard for her children to learn
OL,19,Feffectively.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
