OL,3,CThe tidal wave of desperation I've
OL,4,Cwitnessed reporting on SEND crisis
OL,6,FMum Julie said: "I don't want to go
OL,7,Fthrough my child telling me she's
OL,8,Fpoorly every day and kicking and
OL,9,Fscreaming on the way to school, then
OL,10,Fcoming home from school and going
OL,11,Fstraight to bed because she just can't
OL,12,Ffunction and she just doesn't want to
OL,13,Fbe alive at seven years old."
OL,15,FJulie's son Tom said his experience of
OL,16,Fschool had impacted his mental health.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
