OL,3,CThe tidal wave of desperation I've
OL,4,Cwitnessed reporting on SEND crisis
OL,6,FI have covered this story for years
OL,7,Fnow, and will continue to, but my work
OL,8,Fis one example - many colleagues in
OL,9,FITV News have been doing the same in
OL,10,Ftheir parts of the country.
OL,12,FHopefully this collaborative effort
OL,13,Fwill help families long-term to get
OL,14,Fthe change they are calling for - but,
OL,15,Fmost significantly of all, their
OL,16,Fdetermination, resilience and pure
OL,17,Flove for their children is inspiring
OL,18,Fand deserves our attention.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
